      "end": 4.98,
      "text": "This is a LibraVox recording. All LibraVox recordings are in the public domain.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-001",
      "start": 5.78,
      "end": 11.18,
      "text": "For more information and to find out how you can volunteer, please visit LibraVox.org.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-002",
      "start": 11.8,
      "end": 14.2,
      "text": "Recording by Gitu Milwani.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-003",
      "start": 15.24,
      "end": 18.76,
      "text": "Aseps Fables. Mercury and the Tradesman.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-004",
      "start": 19.9,
      "end": 29.68,
      "text": "When Jupiter was creating man, he told Mercury to make an infusion of lies and to add a little of it to all the other ingredients which went into the making of the tradesmen.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-005",
      "start": 29.68,
      "end": 34.92,
      "text": "Mercury did so and introduced an equal amount into each in turn.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-006",
      "start": 35.5,
      "end": 39.48,
      "text": "The Tallow Chandler, the Green Grocer and the Happadesha in all.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-007",
      "start": 40.02,
      "end": 42.96,
      "text": "Till he came to the horse dealer who was last on the list.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-008",
      "start": 43.58,
      "end": 48.86,
      "text": "When finding that he had a quantity of the infusion still left, he put it all into him.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-009",
      "start": 49.44,
      "end": 54.8,
      "text": "This is why all tradesmen lie more or less, but they none of them lie like the horse dealer.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-010",
      "start": 55.88,
      "end": 58.8,
      "text": "End of Mercury and the Tradesman.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-011",
      "start": 58.8,
      "end": 59.18,
      "text": "End of Mercury and the Tradesman.",
      "note": ""
    }
  ],
